  EffectDiscription_ENG: "Digivolve: 4 from [Magnamon][Opponent\u2019s Turn] When
    an opponent\u2019s Digimon attacks, if a card with [Armor Form] in its traits
    or [X Antibody] is in this Digimon\u2019s digivolution cards, you may switch
    the target of attack to this Digimon. [All Turns] When this Digimon would be
    deleted, you may place the top card of this Digimon on top of your security stack
    face down to prevent that deletion."
